                  <triggerstring n="disp">bestätigt die Stiftung</triggerstring> einer <rs type="fn" role="recipient">ewigen <rs type="org" ref="org__wien-st_philipp_und_st_jakob_kapelle-altar_st_maria-messe_leonhard_poll_QGW_II_I_889_a">Messe</rs></rs> in capella beatorum Philippi et Jacobi, <rs type="event" ref="ev__QGW_II_I_929_men_1">welche Jacobus dictus Poll, pro praesenti rector capelle beate Marie
